source.name: Colorado Plateau Rapid Ecoregion Assessment Management Question H3:  Where are allotments and type of allotment?
source.description: This map shows allotments by ownership type, compiled from datasets obtained from BLM and USFS.  Also shows current and near-term status and long-term potential for change.
